flowchart LR
  %% Diagram 06: Service Communication Map (Protocol + Purpose + Reliability)

  Client[Web/Mobile Client]
  Gateway[API Gateway]
  RT[Realtime Gateway]
  Policy[Auth + Rate Limit + RBAC]
  API[NestJS API]
  PGB[PgBouncer]
  PGW[(PostgreSQL Primary)]
  PGR[(PostgreSQL Replica)]
  RED[(Redis)]
  MEI[(Meilisearch)]
  ONNX[ONNX Runtime]
  OLL[Sahayak Runtime\nOllama Primary]
  GPT[OpenAI GPT Fallback]
  PAY[Payment Providers]
  WA[WhatsApp API]
  PUSH[Web Push and In-App Fallback]
  L3[3PL APIs]
  Retry[Retry Policy\nExponential Backoff + Circuit Breaker]
  Sig[Webhook Signature Verify]
  Idem[Idempotency Keys\nOrders + Payments + Webhooks]
  Obs[Metrics + Logs + Traces]
  Weather[OpenWeatherMap]
  Social[Social APIs\nFacebook/TikTok/YouTube]
  LiveKit[LiveKit SFU]
  CRON[CRON Schedules\nHourly: Category Velocity\n15min: Opportunity Scan\nDaily 6AM: Weather Refresh\nWeekly Sun: GBR Eval]

  Client -->|HTTPS REST\nBusiness Operations| Gateway
  Client -->|WSS Primary\nRealtime Subscriptions| RT
  Client -.SSE Fallback.-> Gateway

  Gateway -->|HTTPS\nAuth, Routing, Throttle| Policy
  Policy -->|Approved Traffic| API
  RT -->|Session Auth| API

  API -->|SQL via Prisma| PGB
  PGB -->|Write Commands| PGW
  PGB -->|Read Queries| PGR
  API <--> |Redis Protocol\nCache, Queue, Pub/Sub| RED
  API <--> |HTTP\nLexical Search Index/Query| MEI
  API <--> |Local Runtime\nForecast Inference| ONNX
  API <--> |HTTP\nLLM Tool Calling| OLL
  OLL -.Tiered Fallback.-> GPT

  API -->|HTTPS\nInitiate Payments| PAY
  PAY -->|Webhook HTTPS| Sig
  Sig -->|Verify Signature + Timestamp| Idem
  Idem -->|Deduplicate and Process| API

  API -->|HTTPS\nTemplated Notifications| WA
  WA -.Delivery Failure Fallback.-> PUSH
  API -->|HTTPS\nCreate/Track Shipments| L3
  L3 -.Timeout/5xx Retry.-> Retry
  Retry -.Replay Safe Operations.-> API

  RT -->|WSS\nOrder Push, Chat, Live Events| Client

  API -->|Telemetry| Obs
  RT -->|Telemetry| Obs

  API -->|HTTPS\nWeather Forecast Fetch| Weather
  API -->|HTTPS\nCatalog and Order Sync| Social
  RT -->|WebSocket\nLive Video Coordination| LiveKit

  CRON -.triggers.-> API

  classDef store fill:#eef6ff,stroke:#2d5aa7,stroke-width:1px;
  classDef control fill:#fff3e2,stroke:#8a4f08,stroke-width:1px;
  class PGB,PGW,PGR,RED,MEI store;
  class Policy,Sig,Idem,Retry control;
